snippet.title: Rock Pit Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the release trailer for Rock Pit. Now available on Google Play.

Rock Pit is a hand drawn, physics platformer. The game features lots of baddies, puzzles, tongue in cheek cut scenes and a heavy metal soundtrack!

Please go to https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.g3rst.rockpit to download your copy.

Go to https://www.g3rst.com for more information.

Music:

Hall Of The Metal King
By Alexander Nakarada
(www.serpentsoundstudios.com)
